												<DIV>Yes, bards can get a lot of "exp" when doing PBAoE.&nbsp; Yes, people can find ways to get mass amonts of exp in this game (groups of quadders, PL's, twinks) IT HAPPENS, and most of those examples get more then bards.&nbsp; </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Another key point you fail to see is that if you mess up once in a AoE the mobs can catch you / bash you / get you dead!!! The risk vs reward is nearly even in my opinion.&nbsp; The risk vs reward in a quad group in lets say fire gets over half an aa per 20minutes and the most are always far away.... thats not fair but i dont see you hitting that with a nerf stick.&nbsp; Leave the HUGE population of bards (yea, thats called sarcasm) alone and fix the client crashes or be thinking of how to fix pvp AGAIN (btw - free tranquil and pok from safe zone status like u said) after the new expansion/spells/aa's come out.&nbsp; </DIV>
																		
