												Another solution is to lower the Dot value if the mobs (and not the bard) are moving or not engaged - i belive the rangers archery has similar penalty - if the mob is moving (and i belive it mean moving a lot not just 0.001 cm) and has no one else as its target (i.e. not engaged) or rooted the arrows do less dmg. This solution is global and is already implemented to other classes to nerf their own solo DPS.<br><br>This will kill AE kite but will keep it in other situations (AE groups or raids).<br><br>Also in this case there is no reason to return the range increase to these songs.
																		
